Sentence: Firstly, doping an MgB 2 bulk with Ti significantly increases the J c of the HIP-processed sample, resulting in a higher trapped field than pristine, undoped samples processed with the same technique.
Secondly, the trapped field of B z = 2.12 T at 5 K and 1.66 T at 15 K for the IG1 sample is the highest reported trapped field in a bulk MgB 2 sample processed by IG.
